Virgin Mary: with Suppliant. Virgin at left, wearing a blue robe and wimple or kerchief, and red shoes; her hand extends over 
                                    a female suppliant kneeling, lower right; suppliant, dressed in gray cape, blue head covering, robe, and pectoral decorated with a red cross; 
                                    hand of god emerges from clouds, upper right.

